Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.51,0:00:40.66,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,to a hidden adventure at the dark bottom of the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.40,0:00:34.51,Credits,,0,0,0,,{\pos(520,256)}Timing\N{\fs40}Galaxy 9000
